    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes comprehensive VANOS servicing and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity and peak variable valve timing performance. The suspension retains its factory-tuned McPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry, offering exceptional turn-in response and communicative feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior shows minor age-appropriate wear, but the mechanical integrity remains the priority for any purist seeking a driver-focused experience.",
